  "prompt": "I got 753 rank in Aiims and I have not attended to 1 at counseling. will I am eligible for second and third counseling?",
  "response": "Congratulations on securing a rank of 753 in the AIIMS entrance examination. Generally, candidates who have not attended the first round of counseling are still eligible to participate in the subsequent rounds of counseling, including the second and third rounds. The specific eligibility criteria and procedures might vary slightly, so it is critical to keep an eye on the official notifications from AIIMS or the organizing body.\n\nTo ensure that you do not miss out on any important updates or deadlines, you should regularly check the official AIIMS counseling website or contact the AIIMS admission office directly for detailed information. This will help you understand the exact process you need to follow to participate in the second and third rounds of counseling.",
